title: IAA Tonight | Kansas City Chiefs DL Carlos Dunlap AND Cleveland Browns Season Preview
description: Kansas City Chiefs DL Carlos Dunlap stops by to discuss his new coach Andy Reid, Patrick Mahomes and the receivers, and how underrated the defense is. Plus, the Browns have a lot of questions heading into the 2022 season, including the impending suspension of QB Deshaun Watson. Can the Browns make the playoffs if Watson is suspended for an extensive period of time?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Carlos Dunlap, Leger Douzable, Ashley Nicole Moss)
